ry entitled DRAWING FIRST BLOOD: CREATING JOHN RAMBO, where the creators of the movie talk about the adaptation of the novel to the screen. Then the usual production notes, cast and crew information, and trailers. all in all, not a bad package. I also recommend the novel and the soundtrack for the excellent closing credits song and Jerry Goldsmith score. <p>FIRST BLOOD<br />(1982, R)<br />John J. Rambo: Sylvester Stallone<br />Col. Sam Trautman: Richard Crenna<br />Sheriff Will Teasle: Brian Dennehy<br />Capt. Dave Kern: Bill McKinney<br />Deputy Sgt. Arthur Galt: Jack Starrett<br />Deputy Balford: Michael Talbott<p>Director: Ted Kotcheff<br />Writers: David Morrell (novel), Michael Kozoll, Will Sackheim, Sylvester Stallone<p>MOVIE: 5<br />VIDEO: 5<br />AUDIO: 5<br />EXTRAS: 5<br />MENUS: 5<br />OVERALL: 5
