the lesson Rocky learned in the third sequel... and have Balboa overcome Drago through speed, dodging, footwork and agility? Instead, we have to believe a man half the size of his opponent overpowered the mutant.<br /><br />Not believable. Entertaining, but unworthy of the series.<br /><br />Jeff Messenger, author of the novel "the Shroud of Torrington."
