rce, a parody, a comedy, an action flick or a drama. They try to put in way too much, so most of it falls flat.<p>The scenes with the attacking Barbies is more creepy like &quot;The Stepford Wives&quot; than it is funny, even though you get the jokes in what are supposed to be comic relief moments.<p>Still, this is well worth watching for the animitronics and for sci fi concepts.
