y with older men being with younger women, you may not like this movie; However, in days of old, this was quite common.<br /><br />  If you like a good movie that is sweet, cute, fun, clever, you will love Gigi, even if you hate musicals.  It has a great story, and great characters, and it is just a lot of fun to watch.  I would say it is pretty close to the quality of "My Fair Lady".  The songs will definitely get stuck in your head (The night they invented Champagne, Thank Heaven For Little Girls, I Remember it Well, ect).<br /><br />  God Bless & *ENJOY* ~Amy
