nd blow.'<br /><br />With the effective use of her sexy, sultry, speaking voice and her confident eyes, Howard Hawks creates a new screen image, and one of the most sizzling yet sexual propositions on film...<br /><br />Lauren Bacall has become heir to our memories of the truly memorable star of the 1940s, and, in her own way, one of them...<br /><br />"To Have or Have Not" was remade as "The Breaking Point" with John Garfield and "The Gun Runners" with Audie Murphy and both were, inferior to the original...
